name: Visible Thoughts: 014
description:
014 of the Visible Thoughts series.

A new week, a new visible thought. Or thoughts. Sometimes I wonder if the act of thinking is simply just picking up the same train as the last. And if that's the case, maybe our entire way of thinking is comprised of just a singular, fluid thought that moulds and shifts and adapts based on the culmination of emotion, desire, and circumstance. And if that's the case, then we're not at all dissimilar to the cosmic web encompassing our entire universe - and, perhaps, multiverse. It all starts at one, and the rest are just branches.
